"><b style="color:#f61f09">P</b>ath to Glory</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/orruk-warclans/#Orruk-Warband-Tables" style="color:#fefefe">Orruk Warband Tables</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/orruk-warclans/#Bonesplitterz-Orruks-and-Boarboys-Followers-Rewards-Table" style="color:#fefefe">Bonesplitterz Orruks and Boarboys Followers Rewards Table</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/orruk-warclans/#Ironjawz-Champion-Rewards-Table" style="color:#fefefe">Ironjawz Champion Rewards Table</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/orruk-warclans/#Bonesplitterz-Champion-Rewards-Table" style="color:#fefefe">Bonesplitterz Champion Rewards Table</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/orruk-warclans/#Ironjawz-Orruks-and-Big-Uns-Followers-Rewards-Table" style="color:#fefefe">Ironjawz Orruks and Big ’Uns Followers Rewards Table</a></div><div class="mw1 i30"><span style="color:#e3f1f2">•&nbsp;</span><a style="color:#fefefe" href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/orruk-warclans/#Orruk-Hero-Followers-Rewards-Table" style="color:#fefefe">Orruk Hero Followers Rewards Table</a></div></div></span></td><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_4.png" style="width:20px"></td></tr><tr><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_7.png" style="width:20px;height:20px"></td><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_6.png" style="height:20px"></td><td background="/aos/img/corners/Corner3_5.png" style="width:20px;height:20px"></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>
