ent00003"><span class="tt kwbu">charge</span> <span class="tt kwbu">phase</span></span> must attempt to charge and must make a <span class="tooltip" data-tooltip-content="#tooltip_content00003"><span class="tt kwbu">charge</span> <span class="tt kwbu">move</span></span> if it is possible for them to do so. In addition, any enemy unit within 3" of this unit cannot <a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/the-rules/the-core-rules#Enemy-Units-and-Retreats">retreat</a>.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class="BreakInsideAvoid"><table max-width="450px" border="0" cellpadding="3" style="border-width:0px"><tbody><tr><td class="impact18" style="text-align:center;vertical-align:top;width:30px">4</td><td><p class="impact18">Shout Down da Magic!</p><span class="ShowFluff legend4">This mob shouts so loudly that it unbinds the spells cast by their enemies.<br><div class="spc"></div></span><p>This unit can attempt to <span class="tooltip" data-tooltip-content="#tooltip_content00015"><span class="tt kwbu">unbind</span></span> 1 spell in the enemy <a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/the-rules/the-core-rules#HERO-PHASE">hero phase</a> (no other units can attempt to unbind that spell).</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class="BreakInsideAvoid"><table max-width="450px" border="0" cellpadding="3" style="border-width:0px"><tbody><tr><td class="impact18" style="text-align:center;vertical-align:top;width:30px">5</td><td><p class="impact18">Extra Warpaint</p><span class="ShowFluff legend4">When this mob gathers for battle, the shamans daub its warriors in an extra layer of warpaint making them especially lucky.<br><div class="spc"></div></span><p>When you use the <a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/orruk-warclans/#Warpaint">Warpaint</a> battle trait for this unit, you can re-roll the dice that determines if a wound or <span class="tooltip" data-tooltip-content="#tooltip_content00004"><span class="tt kwbu">mortal</span> <span class="tt kwbu">wound</span></span> is negated.</p></td><