tip_content00046"><b><p>The <a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/orruk-warclans/#Drakkfoot">DRAKKFOOT</a> and WURRGOG PROPHET keywords are used in following Orruk Warclans warscrolls:</p></b><div style="clear:both; margin-bottom:8px;"><div class="BatRole">Leader</div><div class="BreakInsideAvoid"><div  class="clFl BW BS" style="padding: 1px 10px 1px 15px"><span style="color:#101010">•&nbsp;</span><a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/orruk-warclans/Wurrgog-Prophet" style="color:#101010">Wurrgog Prophet</a></div></div><div style="clear:both"></div></div></span></div><div class="tooltip_templates"><span id="tooltip_content00047"><b><p>The <a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/orruk-warclans/#Drakkfoot">DRAKKFOOT</a> and WARDOKK keywords are used in following Orruk Warclans warscrolls:</p></b><div style="clear:both; margin-bottom:8px;"><div class="BatRole">Leader</div><div class="BreakInsideAvoid"><div  class="clFl BW BS" style="padding: 1px 10px 1px 15px"><span style="color:#101010">•&nbsp;</span><a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/orruk-warclans/Wardokk" style="color:#101010">Wardokk</a></div></div><div style="clear:both"></div></div></span></div><div class="tooltip_templates"><span id="tooltip_content00048"><b><p>The <a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/orruk-warclans/#Drakkfoot">DRAKKFOOT</a> and <a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/the-rules/the-core-rules#WIZARDS">WIZARD</a> keywords are used in following Orruk Warclans warscrolls:</p></b><div style="clear:both; margin-bottom:8px;"><div class="BatRole">Leader</div><div class="BreakInsideAvoid"><div  class="clFl BW BS" style="padding: 1px 10px 1px 15px"><span style="color:#101010">•&nbsp;</span><a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/orruk-warclans/Maniak-Weirdnob" style="color:#101010">Maniak Weirdnob</a></div></div><div style="clear:both"></div><div  class="clFl BW BS" style="padding: 1px 10px 1px 15px"><span style="color:#101010">•&nbsp;</span><a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/orruk-warclans/Wardokk" style="color:#101010">Wardokk</a></div><div style="clear:both"></div><div  class="clFl BW BS" style="padding: 1px 10px 1px 15px"><span style="color:#101010">•&nbsp;</span><a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/orruk-warclans/Wurrgog-Prophet" style="color:#101010">Wurrgog Prophet</a></div><div style="clear:both"></div></div></span></div><div class="tooltip_templates"><span id="tooltip_content00049"><div class="tooltip_header">Arcane Bolt</div><a href="/aos/the-rules/the-core-rules#Arcane-Bolt"><div class="tooltip_link"></div></a><div style="clear:both"></div>
Arcane Bolt has a <a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/the-rules/the-core-rules#Casting-Spells">casting value</a> of 5. If successfully cast, pick an enemy unit within 18" of the caster that is visible to them. That unit suffers 1 <a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/the-rules/the-core-rules#Mortal-Wounds">mortal wound</a>. If the casting roll was 10 or more, the unit suffers D3 mortal wounds instead.
</span></div><div class="tooltip_templates"><span id="tooltip_content00050"><b><p>The <a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/orruk-warclans/#Drakkfoot">DRAKKFOOT</a> and HERO keywords are used in following Orruk Warclans warscrolls:</p></b><div style="clear:both; margin-bottom:8px;"><div class="BatRole">Leader</div><div class="BreakInsideAvoid"><div  class="clFl BW BS" style="padding: 1px 10px 1px 15px"><span style="color:#101010">•&nbsp;</span><a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/orruk-warclans/Maniak-Weirdnob" style="color:#101010">Maniak Weirdnob</a></div></div><div style="clear:both"></div><div  class="clFl BW BS" style="padding: 1px 10px 1px 15px"><span style="color:#101010">•&nbsp;</span><a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/orruk-warclans/Savage-Big-Boss" style="color:#101010">Savage Big Boss</a></div><div style="clear:both"></div><div  class="clFl BW BS" style="padding: 1px 10px 1px 15px"><span style="color:#101010">•&nbsp;</span><a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/orruk-warclans/Wardokk" style="color:#101010">Wardokk</a></div><div style="clear:both"></div><div  class="clFl BW BS" style="padding: 1px 10px 1px 15px"><span style="color:#101010">•&nbsp;</span><a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/orruk-warclans/Wurrgog-Prophet" style="color:#101010">Wurrgog Prophet</a></div><div style="clear:both"></div></div></span></div><div class="tooltip_templates"><span id="tooltip_content00051"><b><p>The <a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/orruk-warclans/#Icebone">ICEBONE</a> keyword is used in following Orruk Warclans warscrolls:</p></b><div style="clear:both; margin-bottom:8px;"><div class="BatRole">None</div><div class="BreakInsideAvoid"><div  class="clFl BW BS" style="padding: 1px 10px 1px 15px"><span style="color:#101010">•&nbsp;</span><a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/orruk-warclans/Savage-Big-Stabbas" style="color:#101010">Savage Big Stabbas</a></div></div><div style="clear:both"></div><div  class="clFl BW BS" style="padding: 1px